inputFiles.beam.dat:
RNDSEED      	89736501     ! Random seed
JPART0       	2            ! Incident particle type
TMAX0      	165.0 0.0       ! Incident energy and energy spread; both in (MeV/nucl)
TCUT0 0 1000  ! energy cutoffs [MeV]
NSTAT       100000    0       ! NSTAT, Step of saving
STRAGG          2            ! Straggling: 0-Off 1-Gauss, 2-Vavilov
MSCAT           2            ! Mult. scatt 0-Off 1-Gauss, 2-Moliere
NUCRE           1            ! Nucl.Reac. switcher: 1-ON, 0-OFF
BEAMPOS 0 0 -50 ! Position of the beam
BEAMDIR 0.0 0.0 ! Direction of the beam
BEAMSIGMA  -0.2 -0.2  ! Beam extension
! no BEAMSAD value
DELTAE   0.01   ! relative mean energy loss per transportation step
USECBEAM   sobp.dat   ! Use custom beam source file
inputFiles.detect.dat:
Geometry Mesh
    Name XZ_map
    X -15 15 300
    Y -1 1 1
    Z -2.25 17.5 200

Geometry Mesh
    Name XY_map
    X -15 15 300
    Y -15 15 300
    Z -0.25 0.25 1

Geometry Mesh
    Name Z_narrow
    X -1 1 1
    Y -1 1 1
    Z -2.25 17.5 200

Filter
    Name Primary
    Z == 1
    A == 1
    GEN == 0
Filter
    Name Protons
    Z == 1
    A == 1
Output
    Filename XZ_map.bdo
    Geo XZ_map
    Quantity Dose 

Output
    Filename XY_map.bdo
    Geo XY_map
    Quantity Dose 

Output
    Filename Z_narrow.bdo
    Geo Z_narrow
    Quantity Fluence 
    Quantity Dose 
    Quantity Dose Protons
    Quantity tLET Protons

Output
    Filename Z_narrow_LET.bdo
    Geo Z_narrow
    Quantity dLET 
    Quantity dLET Primary
    Quantity dLET Protons
    Quantity tLET 
    Quantity tLET Primary
